description: The libraries contained in this experiment come from independent growths of skin keratinocytes primary nuclear extracts, NHEK. They are stranded PE76 Illumina GAIIx RNA-Seq libraries from rRNA-depleted and DSN normalized Poly-A- RNA > 200 nucleotides in size.
